title: can i buy a pixel 5 in Singapore?
content: i have been waiting for the Pixel 5 since the day it launched. Google mentioned that they would release the phone in the second release date which was November 8th which was pushed to December 8th.I have been using google phones since the nexus 3 and i am so used to it. i dont understand why google's supply chain is so weak. Will it be available in Singapore? If not available what is the closest next option?
